etenaitad evāha—sātasaṃpūrṇacakraṃ sākṣāt kṛtvā, yāvadiṣṭaṃ kālaṃ vyavasthāpya, paścāt tasya sarvathaiva pradīpavan nirodhaṃ kṛtvā sthātavyam. yadā punaḥ sattvārthābhilāṣo bhavati, tadā niruddhād eva cakrāntaram utpādya sattvārthaḥ kartavyaḥ. cakrāntarotpāde 'pi ciraniruddhād eva cakrād yathābhavyatayā vineyānāṃ yathābhilaṣitaprāptir bhavatīti ṣaṣṭham.

<commentary>kṛtvetyādi. ṣaṇṇāṃ pakṣāṇām anyatamasya phalasya sādhyatvād yad yad evābhiṣṭaṃ tad eva sākṣāt kṛtvā, paścāt sarvathaiva pradīpavan nirodha uttarakālaṃ sattvārthādiśūnyaḥ sākṣāt kartavyaḥ.

nanu ṣaṭpakṣabhedena ṣaḍ eva nirodhāḥ syuḥ. tat katham eka eva nirodha ity āśaṅkyāha—abhinnetyādi. abhinnaṃ rūpaṃ yasya sa tathā. na hi nirodhānāṃ ṣaṭpakṣalakṣaṇabhede 'pi bhedo 'sti, abhāvaikarūpatayā nirodhasya samānatvāt. ayam arthaḥ—anyatamapakṣaṃ sākṣāt kṛtvā, paścāt tasya santānocchedarūpo nirodha iti saptamaṃ sādhyam.</commentary>